New MDL Commands:(THAT I WILL TOTALLY ADD)
Light
    Create and set a point light source in MDL
    Handle multiple lights
mesh
Set a knob to a certain value
Set all knobs to a value

Save Coordinate System--save stack top to symbol table--use in coordinate system option for shapes
Save knobs--save the current list of knob values--used in tween command
-> Generate start and end imageas from list of knobs

